s numerous locations offer hand dipped milkshakes made with edys ice cream  murderedit on the morning of february   yearold assistant manager terri brooks was found murdered in the kitchen of a fairless hills pennsylvania location she was found badly beaten with a bag over head and a large kitchen knife sticking out of her neck she was most likely killed the night before while she was closing the restaurant the restaurants safe was open and empty which led police to believe she was killed by two unknown people who had robbed three other fast food locations in the area the previous week however after the men were later captured they were able to provide solid alibis for the night brooks died the case went unsolved for  years until dna identified brooks thenfiance alfred keefe as the killer in  keefe was convicted of firstdegree murder and was sentenced to life imprisonment without the possibility of parole the case was featured on cold case files as well as various investigation discovery shows the building has since been converted into a mcdonaldsbp gas station combo locationsedit as of october  there are  total roy rogers restaurants in  states maryland new jersey new york pennsylvania virginia west virginia see alsoedit food portal list of fastfood chicken restaurants referencesedit  httpwwwroyrogersrestaurantscomindexcfm  allbusinesscom  plamondon buys roy rogers trademark retrieved    httproyrogersrestaurantscomfoodbreakfast  wcom  tesgs guide to big chain road food consumption retrieved    httpwwwdesertdispatchcomarticlenewsnewstemplateprintart  retailtrafficmagcom  roys franchisee triggers rebirth retrieved    washingtonbizjournalscom  a burger and a shakeup retrieved    washingtontimescom  roy rogers pulls franchising trigger retrieved    washingtonbizjournalscom plamondon enterprises inc retrieved  dead link  hooverscom roy rogers franchise company llc retrieved    thefranchisemallcom roy rogers retrieved    washingtonpostcom  fairfax judge presided over roy