d to feature roy rogers fried chicken the conversion of the roy rogers chain ended in a customer revolt so serious that they actually aborted the idea and returned the roy rogers brand to stores initially converted the restaurants promoted new flamebroiled hamburgers but they were not the same as the original roy rogers products and they later failed hardees finally sold the remaining roy rogers locations to mcdonalds wendys and boston market between  and  this left  roy rogers franchisees with two dozen freestanding locations in addition to locations owned by hmshost in travel plazas along highways in the northeast filming for the first television commercials advertising roy rogers restaurants took place in the apple valley california area where rogers lived with his family in  and  rogers and friends earl bascom and mel marion were filmed at various locations including the historic las flores ranch in summit valley and the campbell ranch in victorville new ownership relaunchedit roy rogers restaurant in westminster maryland in a former ginos building owned by the plamondon companies remodeled in  roy rogers restaurant in germantown maryland owned by the plamondon companies opened in  plamondon companies took the lead among franchisees in developing products hosting training sessions and shooting new food photography for their stores plamondon companies is run by jim plamondon and peter plamondon jr the two sons of peter plamondon sr head of the restaurant division at marriott when the roy rogers brand was created roy rogers was relaunched as roy rogers franchise company llc in  when plamondon companies bought the trademark and franchise system from imasco the former owner of hardees in  cke restaurants acquired hardees from imasco but imasco held on to the roy rogers trademark and franchise system plamondon negotiated with imasco for three years before a private purchase agreement was reached in  the first new roy rogers restaurant after many years of decline was opened in frederick maryland by plamondon in  based in frederick maryland the plamondon companies is a privately held company with annual revenues of  million in  the plamondon companies opened its doors with their first roy rogers restaurant as of  the plamondon companies own and operate  roy rogers restaurants and oversee  franchise locations in the midatlantic region the company is seeking franchisees to continue roy rogers expansion throughout the midatlantic region key datesedit this article is in a list format that may be better presented using prose you can help by converting this article to prose if appropriate editing help is available august   the first roy rogers opens at  leesburg pike falls church virginia s roy rogers chain flourishes under marriott several hundred franchised and company units open s first long island stores open in greenvale nassau county new york and commack suffolk county new york  stores in uniondale island trees and farmingdale all nassau county new york open  long island store opens in shirley new york in suffolk county  roy rogers in fairfax virginia on little river turnpike at the border of alexandria virginia is robbed in a highprofile case where five employees were herded into the restaurants freezer and shot in the head four people were killed and one survived s franchisee plamondon enterprises inc opens seven and acquires three roy rogers locations  marriott purchases the ginos restaurant chain for  million and converts many of the restaurants to roy rogers  marriott threatens to take the riese family a franchisee to court when they discovered the rieses were reserving space for häagen dazs and godfathers pizza in a property slotted for a times square roy rogers restaurant  marriott decides to get out of the fastfood business and sell its roy rogers howard johnsons bobs big boy and other chains to concentrate on its fastfood operations catering to captive buyers at airports and along turnpikes  a total of  roy rogers locations are in operation—primarily in the northeast and midatlantic states  marriott sells roy rogers to hardees subsidiary of imasco for  million in its plan to exit the fastfood business  hardees converts  roy rogers locations to hardees  due to customer loyalty hardees reconverts  former roy rogers locations back to roy rogers  jordan mcgrath case  taylor inc a new york advertising agency is hired to promote the roy rogers brand  ronald r powell who ran roy rogers from  to  under marriott becomes president of roy rogers and is believed to have influenced hardees decision in dropping its conversion strategy and restoring the chain to its original identity  with much fanfare and a celebrating featuring cowboys and pony rides for children an experimental super roy rogers opens at the vienna virginia location the store features usual roy rogers food items but with added flair such as third pound burgers bbq sauce served with a ladle and an improved dining room with television screens  hardees sells  companyowned roy rogers restaurants in the philadelphia region to boston market for  million  hardees sells  companyowned roy rogers restaurants in the new york region to wendys international inc  hardees sells  companyowned roy rogers restaurants in the baltimorewashington region to mcdonalds for  million  only  roy rogers franchisees remain operating a total of about  units through the northeast including  units in highway travel plazas and  in new york city  cke restaurants carls jr acquires hardees from imasco imasco retains roy rogers trademark due to a franchisee lawsuit  the riese family now franchisees of  roy rogers restaurants sues cke restaurants and imasco for  million claiming the roy rogers chain has been destroyed through a series of marketing errors of epic proportions  cke enters into a management agreement for the six roy rogers restaurants currently operated by hardees cke also agrees to perform services relating to the continued franchise operations of the roy rogers restaurant chain for  million over three years s franchisee plamondon enterprises inc opens two and acquires three roy rogers locations  plamondon enterprises inc opens a new roy rogers prototype unit in frederick maryland  plamondon enterprises inc develops and opens a new roy rogers unit in germantown maryland sugarloaf shopping center in a former burger king  imasco sells roy rogers trademark rights to plamondon enterprises inc roy rogers franchise co  hmshost formerly host marriott services signs agreement to continue operating roy rogers in travel plazas  roy rogers franchise company unveils its roy rogers rides again refranchising growth initiative  roy rogers restaurants launches royrogersrestaurantscom website  roy rogers opens in gaithersburg maryland in a former hardees  todd restaurants inc sign new longterm pioneer franchise agreement for its four roy rogers locations in alexandria virginia  smithgifford is selected as the agency of record for roy rogers restaurants  roy rogers restaurants rank th in the franchise times  to watch in   roy rogers opens in ranson west virginia and westminster maryland  super value ct llc enters into a longterm franchise agreement for a roy rogers location in north stonington connecticut  roy rogers opens in north stonington connecticut on january    roy rogers opens in the renovated pennsylvania turnpike lehigh valley allentown service plaza  roy rogers opens a second location in germantown maryland fox chapel shopping center on january   in a former wendys  roy rogers closes in manchester connecticut leaving one restaurant in connecticut  roy rogers closes in penn station leaving one restaurant in new york city the last remaining location in new york is directly across the street from penn station on seventh avenue  roy rogers restaurants redesigns royrogersrestaurantscom website  roy rogers restaurants creates official profiles on facebook twitter and youtube  last roy rogers in delaware closes on december   for delaware house service plaza redevelopment it was replaced with burger king on june    last roy rogers on long island closes on november    last roy rogers in ohio located on roney lane in mt carmel an eastern suburb of cincinnati changes its name to roneys  retains a modified roy rogers sign at this time  roy rogers opens in burtonsville maryland in the new burtonsville town square shopping center  roy rogers opens in la plata maryland at  crain highway in a former arbys  roy rogers opens in waldorf md  roy rogers opens in rockville maryland at  rockville pike  last roy rogers in new york city located at th avenue and west nd street closes in january   roy rogers opens in winchester va  roy rogers opens in a former arbys location at  route  in franklin nj  roy rogers opens its th store on md in gambrills md  roy rogers opens in aspen hill maryland at  georgia avenue  roy rogers plans to open off of magothy beach road in pasadena md  roy rogers opens in former chicken addictionkfc location in flemington nj  roy rogers opens in brick nj  roy rogers opens in former arbyskfc location in edison nj products and servicesedit roy rogers restaurant at the indian castle service plaza on the new york state thruway popular items on the menu are roast beef sandwiches and fried chicken which was advertised by roy rogers under the pappy parker name in the s using a cartoon prospector the pappy parker name was inherited from marriotts original hot shoppes chain other signature items at roy rogers are the gold rush chicken sandwich a fried chicken breast with bacon a slice of monterey jack cheese and a honeybased bbq sauce and the doubler bar burger a cheeseburger with ham the side items featured at roy rogers are french fries baked potatoes mashed potatoes with gravy baked beans coleslaw side salad fruit cup and baked apples though standard roy rogers locations serve food in a typical fastfood fashion some locations such as the locations that were formerly jr hot shoppes and the franchises located throughout midatlantic highway reststops serve the food in a cafeteriastyle an exception is the allentown service plaza on the pennsylvania turnpikes northeast extension which serves its customers in the typical fastfood fashion since it reopened in may  the entire service plaza had been rebuilt from its original form which included cafeteriastyle serving in the cafeteriastyle restaurants customers push their trays on rails past stations stocked with prewrapped packages of hamburgers cheeseburgers and roastbeef sandwiches a feature of this chain in any of the locations is the fixins bar which features numerous condiments because of this sandwich items are delivered without any of the customary garnishes after selecting and paying for these items patrons can garnish them to their own taste at the fixins bar with such items as ketchup bbq sauce mayonnaise horseradish sauce lettuce tomatoes pickles and onions numerous locations offer hand dipped milkshakes made with edys ice cream  murderedit on the morning of february   yearold assistant manager terri brooks was found murdered in the kitchen of a fairless hills pennsylvania location she was found badly beaten with a bag over head and a large kitchen knife sticking out of her neck she was most likely killed the night before while she was closing the restaurant the restaurants safe was open and empty which led police to believe she was killed by two unknown people who had robbed three other fast food locations in the area the previous week however after the men were later captured they were able to provide solid alibis for the night brooks died the case went unsolved for  years until dna identified brooks thenfiance alfred keefe as the killer in  keefe was convicted of firstdegree murder and was sentenced to life imprisonment without the possibility of parole the case was featured on cold case files as well as various investigation discovery shows the building has since been converted into a mcdonaldsbp gas station combo locationsedit as of october  there are  total roy rogers restaurants in  states maryland new jersey new york pennsylvania virginia west virginia see alsoedit food portal list of fastfood chicken restaurants referencesedit  httpwwwroyrogersrestaurantscomindexcfm  allbusinesscom  plamondon buys roy rogers trademark retrieved    httproyrogersrestaurantscomfoodbreakfast  wcom  tesgs guide to big chain road food consumption retrieved    httpwwwdesertdispatchcomarticlenewsnewstemplateprintart  retailtrafficmagcom  roys franchisee triggers rebirth retrieved    washingtonbizjournalscom  a burger and a shakeup retrieved    washingtontimescom  roy rogers pulls franchising trigger retrieved    washingtonbizjournalscom plamondon enterprises inc retrieved  dead link  hooverscom roy rogers franchise company llc retrieved    thefranchisemallcom roy rogers retrieved    washingtonpostcom  fairfax judge presided over roy rogers murder case the washington post retrieved    nytimescom  marriott ginos bid backed by boards the new york times retrieved    rieserestaurantscom branding an empire archived from the original on may   retrieved    nytimescom  murray riese  restaurateur who developed the food court the new york times retrieved    nytimescom  marriott plans retreat from fastfood wars the new york times retrieved    nytimescom  company news roy rogers chain is sold to hardees the new york times retrieved    geocitiescomroyrogerswb history archived from the original on  retrieved    nytimescom  the media business advertising  addenda roy rogers account to jordan mcgrath the new york times retrieved    findarticlescom  powell returns to roy rogers as president nations restaurant news retrieved    findarticlescom  boston chicken buys  roy rogers units hardees exits philadelphia restates commitment to stronger markets nations restaurant news retrieved    nytimescom  company news hardees is set to sell its roy rogers restaurants the new york times retrieved    n