their product line because they needed the trim scraps for boiler fuel  in the early years things were so tough that peter rogers worked out as a millwright and saw filer to earn money to send back to peter johnson to keep the mill going peters son emory rogers joined the firm in  after serving in word war i  emorys sons tom and jim rogers joined the firm after serving in world war ii  toms son peter t rogers the fourth generation of rogers joined the firm after his graduation from college in  and is now the company president under the guidance of tom jim and peter and with the hard work and dedication of the people working at marion plywood corporation the plant has grown from a few old unheated wood buildings with  workers in  making only excelsior and cheese boxes to its present size work force and diversified line of products today our plywood is used in hardwood floor panels window parts drums and pianos just to name a few through marion plywood corporations wholly owned subsidiary great lakes veneer inc wood veneers are used by flooring manufacturers furniture manufacturers door and window manufacturers and countless other plywood finished goods marion plywood corporation  s parkview ave  po box  marion wi  phone   fax  fsc certificate code scscoc fsc license number fscc